110
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:47,820
[Father, Mother, don't worry about me.
Take care.]

111
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,830
However, the Yue State's secret techniques
are remarkable.

112
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,490
If you can receive treatment there,

113
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:52,830
[My dear parents, Please forgive me
for leaving without saying goodbye.]

114
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:53,370
there might still be a glimmer of hope.

115
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:55,840
[With the imperial court's secret order,
I'm afraid I'll be away for a few years.]

116
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,930
[Father, Mother, don't worry about me.
Take care.]

117
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:43,270
If you had stayed by my side obediently,
you would have recovered by now.

118
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:44,440
But look at you now.

119
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:47,070
You've really made yourself become blind.

120
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:49,720
This time,
it'll be hard to cure your eyes.

121
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:14,960
Who's there?

122
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,030
Who are you?

123
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:17,440
Who are you?

124
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,360
You'd rather die than let me save you.

125
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,200
I can't let you know who I am.

126
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,870
I'm a female doctor.

127
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,550
I can cure your disease.

128
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:28,150
If you can cure my eyes,

129
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:31,130
I'll reward you with a large sum of money.

130
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,720
I don't want money.

131
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,280
Then what do you want?

132
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,860
I haven't decided yet.

133
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,630
May I ask for a wish?

134
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,580
No matter what you ask for,

135
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,850
I will spare no efforts to fulfill it.

136
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,600
Your Majesty.

137
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:10,120
Your people
have repeatedly come to invite me,

138
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,790
saying you're not used to this new place
and your condition is worsening.

139
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:15,790
I didn't expect
you would still have energy to do this.

140
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,390
If they hadn't said that,

141
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:20,350
would you have come to see me?

142
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,550
My illness

143
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,000
has truly become incurable.

144
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,750
I just want to
simply have a meal with you.

145
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,770
After this meal,

146
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,270
I have something important to tell you.

147
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,330
What else is there?

148
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,270
Just say it all at once.

149
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:39,000
It's about the late emperor
and the Eldest Prince.

150
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:42,270
I think you'll certainly be interested.

151
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,870
I made all these dishes.

152
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,240
Taste them now.

153
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,750
Do they taste the same as before?

154
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:57,200
Do you still remember this?

155
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,670
When you were 6 years old,

156
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,870
