and saying that you wanted to eat meat,

157
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:03,960
so I made this steamed venison for you.

158
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,550
You were so happy eating it back then.

159
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,320
Yes.

160
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,960
But the happiness didn't last long.

161
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,090
Then you put me into a medicine barrel,

162
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,870
saying that this time, the medicine

163
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:16,070
would be more effective when I got full.

164
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,750
Just consider
that a dying person's words are kind.

165
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,960
I've done all these things

166
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,720
truly for your own good.

167
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:25,240
If you don't want to eat them,

168
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,510
I won't force you.

169
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,290
Just consider this as sitting here

170
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,750
with me for a while.

171
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,390
Jun Che's changes in these past few days

172
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,050
have really been too strange.

173
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,390
Now that I'm thinking carefully about it,

174
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:45,320
since Jun Che's mother appeared,

175
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,030
everything seems to

176
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:48,560
have returned
to the path of my previous life.

177
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,670
Che.

178
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,840
Now in the palace,

179
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,390
